RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 5F All Weather Track CR: 64. Maiden Claiming Purse 37000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 118 lbs. Claiming Price $35,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: HEAVEN IN MIND stalked in the four path, was coaxed midway around the turn, got floated out to the nine path into the stretch, and rallied past an inner pair in the final sixteenth to win. KOZEM was prompted along in the three path, ran on from said position into the lane, bid into the final furlong, but was out-finished by the outer eventual winner to place. WELLTON GIRL raced off the pace in the two path, tipped out to the five path while under a drive into the stretch, and kept on for show. MISS ATHLETIC broke well to set an open pace in the two path, but drifted out to the eight path in upper stretch, and yielded late. BRASSIC was wellback in the three path and made no impact from the six path down the lane. CAP IS BACK broke a step slow, trailed in the two path early, and did not threaten. LAS COLINAS broke in at the start, chased in the three path, tipped inside rounding the turn, but was empty.
